flowchart TD
    ServerStart([Server Startup]) --> InitServices[Initialize Background Services]

    InitServices --> QBSync[QuickBooks Sync Service]
    InitServices --> FESync[FieldEdge Customer Sync]
    InitServices --> PBSync[Pricebook Sync Service]
    InitServices --> AgreementRenew[Agreement Renewal Service]
    InitServices --> MaintenanceRemind[Maintenance Reminder Service]
    InitServices --> ReviewReq[Review Request Service]
    InitServices --> BouncieSync[Bouncie Location Sync]
    InitServices --> WeatherSync[Weather Update Service]
    InitServices --> StripeSync[Stripe Product Sync]

    QBSync --> QBSchedule{Schedule:<br/>Every 6 Hours}
    QBSchedule -->|Trigger| QBRun[Run QuickBooks Sync]

    QBRun --> QBCheckConnection{QuickBooks<br/>Connected?}
    QBCheckConnection -->|No| QBSkip[Skip Sync]
    QBCheckConnection -->|Yes| QBRefreshToken{Token<br/>Expired?}

    QBRefreshToken -->|Yes| QBRefresh[Refresh Access Token]
    QBRefreshToken -->|No| QBProceed[Proceed with Sync]
    QBRefresh --> QBProceed

    QBProceed --> QBSyncCustomers[Sync Customers to QuickBooks<br/>Create/Update]
    QBSyncCustomers --> QBSyncInvoices[Sync Unpaid Invoices<br/>to QuickBooks]
    QBSyncInvoices --> QBSyncPayments[Sync Recent Payments<br/>to QuickBooks]
    QBSyncPayments --> QBLog[Log Sync Results<br/>Success/Failure Counts]
    QBLog --> QBComplete[Update Last Sync Time]

    QBSkip --> QBWait[Wait for Next Schedule]
    QBComplete --> QBWait

    FESync --> FESchedule{Schedule:<br/>Every 5 Minutes}
    FESchedule -->|Trigger| FERun[Run FieldEdge Sync]

    FERun --> FEFetchSheets[Fetch Google Sheets<br/>Customer Data]
    FEFetchSheets --> FESuccess{API Call<br/>Success?}

    FESuccess -->|Error| FELogError[Log Error & Skip]
    FESuccess -->|Success| FECalculateHash[Calculate Data Hash]

    FECalculateHash --> FEDataChanged{Hash<br/>Changed?}
    FEDataChanged -->|No| FEUpdateCheck[Update Last Check Time]
    FEDataChanged -->|Yes| FEProcessRows[Process All Rows]

    FEProcessRows --> FECacheUpdate[Update In-Memory Cache<br/>for Fast Search]
    FECacheUpdate --> FEUpdateTimestamp[Update Last Sync Time]
    FEUpdateTimestamp --> FEWait[Wait for Next Schedule]

    FELogError --> FEWait
    FEUpdateCheck --> FEWait

    PBSync --> PBSchedule{Schedule:<br/>Every 1 Minute}
    PBSchedule -->|Trigger| PBRun[Run Pricebook Sync]

    PBRun --> PBFetchSheets[Fetch Google Sheets<br/>Package Pricing]
    PBFetchSheets --> PBSuccess{API Call<br/>Success?}

    PBSuccess -->|Error| PBLogError[Log Error & Skip]
    PBSuccess -->|Success| PBParsePackages[Parse Package Data<br/>All Tonnages & Tiers]

    PBParsePackages --> PBUpsertDB[Upsert to pricebook_packages<br/>Update Prices]
    PBUpsertDB --> PBUpdateItems[Update Related Line Items<br/>in Active Quotes]
    PBUpdateItems --> PBLog[Log Sync Results]
    PBLog --> PBWait[Wait for Next Schedule]

    PBLogError --> PBWait

    AgreementRenew --> ARSchedule{Schedule:<br/>Daily at 2 AM}
    ARSchedule -->|Trigger| ARRun[Run Agreement Renewal Check]

    ARRun --> ARQueryExpiring[Query Expiring Agreements<br/>expirationDate <= 30 days]
    ARQueryExpiring --> ARForEach{For Each<br/>Agreement}

    ARForEach -->|Agreement| ARCheckAutoRenew{Auto Renew<br/>Enabled?}
    ARCheckAutoRenew -->|No| ARSendReminder[Send Renewal Reminder<br/>Email to Customer]
    ARCheckAutoRenew -->|Yes| ARCheckPayment{Payment Method<br/>on File?}

    ARCheckPayment -->|No| ARSendReminder
    ARCheckPayment -->|Yes| ARProcessRenewal[Process Auto Renewal<br/>Charge Card via Stripe]

    ARProcessRenewal --> ARPaymentSuccess{Payment<br/>Success?}
    ARPaymentSuccess -->|No| ARSendFailedEmail[Send Payment Failed Email]
    ARPaymentSuccess -->|Yes| ARCreateNewAgreement[Create New Agreement<br/>1-Year Extension]

    ARCreateNewAgreement --> ARSendConfirmation[Send Renewal Confirmation<br/>Email with Invoice]
    ARSendConfirmation --> ARNextAgreement{More<br/>Agreements?}
    ARSendReminder --> ARNextAgreement
    ARSendFailedEmail --> ARNextAgreement

    ARNextAgreement -->|Yes| ARForEach
    ARNextAgreement -->|No| ARLog[Log Renewal Results]
    ARLog --> ARWait[Wait for Next Schedule]

    MaintenanceRemind --> MRSchedule{Schedule:<br/>Daily at 9 AM}
    MRSchedule -->|Trigger| MRRun[Run Maintenance Reminder Check]

    MRRun --> MRQueryDue[Query Agreements<br/>with Upcoming Visits]
    MRQueryDue --> MRForEach{For Each<br/>Visit Due}

    MRForEach -->|Visit| MRCheckNotified{Reminder Sent<br/>< 7 Days?}
    MRCheckNotified -->|Yes| MRSkip[Skip Reminder]
    MRCheckNotified -->|No| MRBuildMessage[Build Reminder Message<br/>Visit Type, Date]

    MRBuildMessage --> MRCustomerConsent{Customer<br/>SMS Opt-In?}
    MRCustomerConsent -->|Yes| MRSendSMS[Send SMS via Textline]
    MRCustomerConsent -->|No| MRSendEmail[Send Email via Resend]

    MRSendSMS --> MRLogNotification[Log Reminder Sent<br/>Update lastReminderAt]
    MRSendEmail --> MRLogNotification

    MRLogNotification --> MRNext{More<br/>Visits?}
    MRSkip --> MRNext

    MRNext -->|Yes| MRForEach
    MRNext -->|No| MRLog[Log Reminder Results]
    MRLog --> MRWait[Wait for Next Schedule]

    ReviewReq --> RRSchedule{Schedule:<br/>Daily at 6 PM}
    RRSchedule -->|Trigger| RRRun[Run Review Request Check]

    RRRun --> RRQueryCompleted[Query Completed Work Orders<br/>completedAt = Yesterday]
    RRQueryCompleted --> RRForEach{For Each<br/>Work Order}

    RRForEach -->|Work Order| RRCheckPaid{Invoice<br/>Paid?}
    RRCheckPaid -->|No| RRSkip[Skip Review Request]
    RRCheckPaid -->|Yes| RRCheckRecent{Review Request<br/>< 90 Days?}

    RRCheckRecent -->|Yes| RRSkip
    RRCheckRecent -->|No| RRBuildReview[Build Review Request SMS<br/>Google Review Link]

    RRBuildReview --> RRCheckPhone{Customer<br/>Phone Valid?}
    RRCheckPhone -->|No| RRSkip
    RRCheckPhone -->|Yes| RRSendSMS[Send SMS via Textline]

    RRSendSMS --> RRSuccess{SMS<br/>Sent?}
    RRSuccess -->|Error| RRLogError[Log Error]
    RRSuccess -->|Success| RRLogSent[Log to crm_message_log<br/>Update lastReviewRequestAt]

    RRLogSent --> RRNext{More<br/>Work Orders?}
    RRLogError --> RRNext
    RRSkip --> RRNext

    RRNext -->|Yes| RRForEach
    RRNext -->|No| RRLog[Log Review Request Results]
    RRLog --> RRWait[Wait for Next Schedule]

    BouncieSync --> BSSchedule{Schedule:<br/>Every 15 Minutes}
    BSSchedule -->|Trigger| BSRun[Run Bouncie Location Sync]

    BSRun --> BSCheckConnection{Bouncie<br/>Connected?}
    BSCheckConnection -->|No| BSSkip[Skip Sync]
    BSCheckConnection -->|Yes| BSRefreshToken{Token<br/>Expired?}

    BSRefreshToken -->|Yes| BSRefresh[Refresh OAuth Token]
    BSRefreshToken -->|No| BSProceed[Proceed with Sync]
    BSRefresh --> BSProceed

    BSProceed --> BSFetchVehicles[Fetch Vehicle List<br/>from Bouncie API]
    BSFetchVehicles --> BSForEach{For Each<br/>Vehicle}

    BSForEach -->|Vehicle| BSGetLocation[Get Current Location<br/>GPS Coordinates]
    BSGetLocation --> BSSaveLocation[Save to vehicle_locations<br/>Timestamp, Lat/Lng]
    BSSaveLocation --> BSUpdateTech[Update Tech Location<br/>if Assigned]

    BSUpdateTech --> BSNextVehicle{More<br/>Vehicles?}
    BSNextVehicle -->|Yes| BSForEach
    BSNextVehicle -->|No| BSLog[Log Sync Results]

    BSLog --> BSWait[Wait for Next Schedule]
    BSSkip --> BSWait

    WeatherSync --> WSSchedule{Schedule:<br/>Every 4 Hours}
    WSSchedule -->|Trigger| WSRun[Run Weather Update]

    WSRun --> WSGetLocations[Get Active Service Areas<br/>Unique Zip Codes]
    WSGetLocations --> WSForEach{For Each<br/>Location}

    WSForEach -->|Location| WSFetchForecast[Fetch Forecast<br/>from Weather API]
    WSFetchForecast --> WSSuccess{API Call<br/>Success?}

    WSSuccess -->|Error| WSLogError[Log Error & Skip]
    WSSuccess -->|Success| WSParseForecast[Parse 7-Day Forecast]

    WSParseForecast --> WSSaveForecast[Save to weather_forecasts<br/>Temperature, Conditions]
    WSSaveForecast --> WSAnalyzeImpact{Extreme<br/>Weather?}

    WSAnalyzeImpact -->|Yes| WSCreateAlert[Create Weather Alert<br/>Notify Dispatchers]
    WSAnalyzeImpact -->|No| WSSkipAlert[Skip Alert]

    WSCreateAlert --> WSNext{More<br/>Locations?}
    WSSkipAlert --> WSNext
    WSLogError --> WSNext

    WSNext -->|Yes| WSForEach
    WSNext -->|No| WSLog[Log Weather Update Results]
    WSLog --> WSWait[Wait for Next Schedule]

    StripeSync --> SSSchedule{Schedule:<br/>On Server Start<br/>+ Manual Trigger}
    SSSchedule -->|Trigger| SSRun[Run Stripe Product Sync]

    SSRun --> SSFetchProducts[Fetch All Products<br/>from Stripe API]
    SSFetchProducts --> SSSuccess{API Call<br/>Success?}

    SSSuccess -->|Error| SSLogError[Log Error]
    SSSuccess -->|Success| SSForEach{For Each<br/>Product}

    SSForEach -->|Product| SSUpsertProduct[Upsert to stripe_products]
    SSUpsertProduct --> SSFetchPrices[Fetch Prices for Product<br/>from Stripe API]
    SSFetchPrices --> SSUpsertPrices[Upsert to stripe_prices]

    SSUpsertPrices --> SSNext{More<br/>Products?}
    SSNext -->|Yes| SSForEach
    SSNext -->|No| SSLog[Log Sync Results]

    SSLog --> SSComplete[Sync Complete]
    SSLogError --> SSComplete

    style ServerStart fill:#e1f5ff
    style QBSync fill:#fff3cd
    style FESync fill:#fff3cd
    style PBSync fill:#fff3cd
    style AgreementRenew fill:#d4edda
    style MaintenanceRemind fill:#d4edda
    style ReviewReq fill:#d4edda
    style BouncieSync fill:#f8d7da
    style WeatherSync fill:#f8d7da
    style StripeSync fill:#e2e3e5
